{dropDownValues?.pfList.map((option) => ( {option.pf_name} ))}

{dropDownValues?.ldList.map((option) => ( {option.ld_name} ))}

{dropDownValues?.octroiList.map((option) => ( {option.octroi_name} ))}

); }; export default AccountTNC;
